OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776345056
OL,3,CCause of death unknown for elderly
OL,4,Cwoman found in freezer
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of an 89-
OL,7,Fyear-old woman has heard further
OL,8,Finvestigations are required to
OL,9,Fdetermine the cause.
OL,11,FThe body of Sylvia Phillips was found
OL,12,Fin a freezer at a house in Poplar
OL,13,FCrescent, Porthcawl on February 17 by
OL,14,Fofficers from South Wales Police.
OL,16,FAt the inquest, the Coroner's officer
OL,17,FJoanne Webb said a post-mortem
OL,18,Fexamination had been carried out at
OL,19,Fthe University Hospital of Wales in
OL,20,FCardiff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
