FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776345056
OL,3,CCause of death unknown for elderly
OL,4,Cwoman found in freezer
OL,6,FBut the cause of her death is not yet
OL,7,Fknown.
OL,9,FThe Senior Coroner for South Wales
OL,10,FCentral Graeme Hughes adjourned the
OL,11,Finquest until a later date, which is
OL,12,Fyet to be set.
OL,14,FMs Phillips' son, Christopher
OL,15,FPhillips, aged 60, was arrested in
OL,16,FFebruary following the discovery of
OL,17,Fthe body.
OL,19,FHe appeared at Cardiff Crown Court
OL,20,Flast month and was charged with
OL,21,Fpreventing a lawful burial.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
